column1: Beautiful & luxurious apartment at great location
column2: I rent out a very sunny and bright apartment only 7 minutes walking distance to the metro station. The apartment has a spacious living room with a kitchen, one bedroom and a bathroom with mit bath. A terrace can be used in summer.
Peaceful studio in the most wanted area in town. Quiet house Near of everything. Completely renovated. Lovely neighbourhood, lot of trendy shops, restaurants and bars in a walking distance.
